snippet.title: myFloppy Online Trailer
snippet.description:
myFloppy Online - the virtual pet revolution that invites gamers to step into the wacky digital world of Floppy- the world’s most beloved floppy disk!

Checkout myFloppy on Steam here: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1584300/Strangestios_myFloppy_Online
Checkout myFloppy on Itch.io here: https://thestrangest.itch.io/myfloppy
